, benefits, supplies), we have added a 3% surcharge to all checks. We do this in lieu of increased menu prices. You may request to have this taken off your check, should you choose. **Consuming raw or undercooked meats, poultry, seafood, shellfish, or eggs may increase your risk of foodborne illness, especially if you have certain medical conditions To make a reservation, use the widget below or call  Joe's Washington, D.C. at  202-489-0140 .\n\t\t Valet Parking Available or  Book with Spothero Sunday 11:30AM - 9:00PM Monday - Saturday 11:30AM - 10:00PM We use cookies to provide the best experience on our website. By continuing to use our site you agree to  our updated privacy policy . for every $100 in gift cards you buy No holiday meal\u00a0is complete without a delicious pie from Joe's. Orders must be placed by Sunday, November 19 for pickup on Tuesday, November 21 or Wednesday, November 22.", "size": 50887, "depth": 2, "download_timeout": 180.0, "download_slot": "www.joes.net", "download_latency": 0.9348180294036865, "status": 200, "links_url": "https://www.joes.net/dc/menu/all-day/#main@@https://www.joes.net/chicago/@@https://www.joes.net/las-vegas/@@https://www.joes.net/dc/@@https://www.joes.net@@https://www.joes.net/dc@@https://www.joes.net/dc/reservations/@@https://www.joes.net/dc/menu/@@https://www.joes.net/dc/private-parties/@@https://www.joes.net/dc/carry-out-delivery/@@https://www.joes.net/dc/whats-crackin/@@https://joes.cashstar.com/@@https://www.joes.net/dc/menu/all-day/@@https://www.joes.net/dc/menu/dinner-market-card/@@https://www.joes.net/dc/menu/lunch-market-card/@@https://www.joes.net/dc/menu/dessert/@@https://www.joes.net/dc/menu/wine/@@https://www.joes.net/dc/menu/cocktail-beer/@@https://www.joes.net/dc/menu/gluten-free-vegetarian/@@https://www.joes.net/dc/menu/kids/@@https://tinyurl.com/y9sk3cqh@@https://spothero.app.link/ts1p2NqSe1?kind=destination&id=84048&$3p=a_hasoffers&$affiliate_json=http%3A%2F%2Ftracking.spothero.com%2Faff_c%3Foffer_id%3