Sept-2384-1.jpg", "width": 1440, "height": 705}, {"@type": "BreadcrumbList", "@id": "https://www.joes.net/dc/private-parties/#breadcrumb", "itemListElement": [{"@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://www.joes.net/"}, {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Washington, D.C.", "item": "https://www.joes.net/dc/"}, {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Private Parties"}]}, {"@type": "WebSite", "@id": "https://www.joes.net/#website", "url": "https://www.joes.net/", "name": "Joe&#039;s Seafood, Prime Steak &amp; Stone Crab", "description": "", "potentialAction": [{"@type": "SearchAction", "target": {"@type": "EntryPoint", "urlTemplate": "https://www.joes.net/?s={search_term_string}"}, "query-input": "required name=search_term_string"}], "inLanguage": "en-US"}], "body_text": "to Continue Located just steps from the White House, Joe\u2019s provides the ideal setting for intimate gatherings or large parties with accommodations for up to 150 guests. Private dining menus feature fresh seafood and prime steaks with our signature sides and freshly baked pies. Tuxedo-clad restaurant style service allows guests to select their entree at the time of the event. Our dedicated event planners will ensure your event is both exceptional and effortless. Completely private seating for up to 70 guests, equipped with audio-visual capabilities including two flat screen televisions, satellite cable, and high speed wireless internet. Completely private seating for up to 40 guests at round tables or 22 guests at one long table. Equipped with audio-visual capabilities including two flat screen televisions and satellite cable.  At the top of the grand staircase, the mezzanine level is devoted to private dining and equipped with a dedicated kitchen and full bar. The Gigi Room, our largest room, can accommodate up to 112 guests seated or 150 guests reception-style. The Gigi Room is equipped with 4, 75\u201d  at screen monitors with HDMI connectivity or DirectTV access as well as a wireless microphone. Our popular South Beach Room can accommodate up to 30 guest for a seated dinner. With ornamental glass doors to reveal or conceal the bar below and full audio visual capabilities, the room is perfect for social or business events. With a custom solid walnut and mahogany table, Grace\u2019s Room is perfect for high-powered business meetings. The room offers completely private dining for up to 22 guests, comfortable boardroom-style chairs and full audio-visual capabilities. Offering complete privacy with a custom walnut and mahogany table, full audio visual capabilities and seating for up to 16 guests, Jo Ann\u2019s Room is the perfect place for your next meeting. With restored floor to ceiling millwork, Jesse\u2019s Room offers intimate seating for up to ten guests.  Click on a room to learn more AV Equipment | Flat Screen TV | Laptop Connections | Wireless Microphone  I feel lucky to work at something that truly makes me happy.  I started my hospitality career many years ago in New York and have been planning events in Washington D.C. since moving here in 2000. I joined the Joe\u2019s Seafood, Prime Steak and Stone Crab team in 2016.  It is a great feeling to work with such professionals who share the same goal of taking care of the guest. Meeting and exceeding guest\u2019s needs and expectations is the most rewarding part of what we do.  Each day I have the chance to help people celebrate business and social events in a beautiful restaurant with amazing food, wine and service. There is no better feeling than seeing a guest return month after month and year after year.\r\n I've worked in restaurants my whole life. I started as a dishwasher and busser in a small bed and breakfast in New Jersey. Since then, I've worked in New York, Philadelphia, San Diego, and now here in Washington, DC where I plan to stay. I started at Joe's shortly after we opened in 2014 and it's been the best restaurant family I've ever been a part of. I have an immense passion for hospitality and strive to take care of guests as if they are dining in my home. I am thankful for the caring, strong, and incredible staff we have at Joe's. It's incredible to work for the best restaurant in Washington, DC especially with help from my amazing teammates and employees! Valet Parking Available or  Book with Spothero Sunday 11:30AM - 9:00PM Monday - Saturday 11:30AM - 10:00PM We use cookies to provide the best experience on our website. By continuing to use our site you agree to  our updated privacy policy . for every $100 in gift cards you buy No holiday meal\u00a0is complete without a delicious pie from Joe's. Orders must be placed by Sunday, November 19 for pickup on Tuesday, November 21 or Wednesday, November 22.", "size": 47213, "depth": 2, "download_timeout": 180.0, "download_slot": "www.joes.net", "download_latency": 0.848351001739502, "status": 200, "links_url": "https://www.joes.net/dc/private-parties/#main@@https://www.joes.net/chicago/@@https://www.joes.net/las-vegas/@@https://www.joes.net/dc/@@https://www.joes.net@@https://www.joes.net/dc@@https://www.joes.net/dc/reservations/@@https://www.joes.net/dc/menu/@@https://www.joes.net/dc/private-parties/@@https://www.joes.net/dc/carry-out-delivery/@@https://www.joes.net/dc/whats-crackin/@@https://joes.cashstar.com/@@https://www.joes.net/dc/menu/private-dining/@@https://www.tripleseat.com@@https://tinyurl.com/y9sk3cqh@@https://spothero.app.link/ts1p2NqSe1?kind=destination&id=84048&$3p=a_hasoffers&$affiliate_json=http%3A%2F%2Ftracking.spothero.com%2Faff_c%3Foffer_id%3D1%26aff_id%3D1568%26source%3Djoesseafooddc%26format%3Djson@@https://tinyurl.com/y9sk3cqh@@https://www.joes.net/dc/newsletter-mobile-club@@https://www.joes.net/dc/contact@@https://www.facebook.com/joesstonedc/@@https://twitter.com/Joes_DC@@https://www.instagram.com/joesseafood/@@https://www.lettuce.com@@https://joes.cashstar.com@@https://harri.com/LEYE?filters=brands%253D4489669%25252C4489662%25252C448965