Url": "https://storage.googleapis.com/joesseafood_bucket/wp-content/uploads/Joes_Sept-2384-1.jpg", "width": 1440, "height": 705}, {"@type": "BreadcrumbList", "@id": "https://www.joes.net/las-vegas/private-parties/#breadcrumb", "itemListElement": [{"@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://www.joes.net/"}, {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Las Vegas", "item": "https://www.joes.net/las-vegas/"}, {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Private Parties"}]}, {"@type": "WebSite", "@id": "https://www.joes.net/#website", "url": "https://www.joes.net/", "name": "Joe&#039;s Seafood, Prime Steak &amp; Stone Crab", "description": "", "potentialAction": [{"@type": "SearchAction", "target": {"@type": "EntryPoint", "urlTemplate": "https://www.joes.net/?s={search_term_string}"}, "query-input": "required name=search_term_string"}], "inLanguage": "en-US"}], "body_text": "to Continue Located in The Forum Shops at Caesars Palace, Joe\u2019s provides the ideal setting for intimate gatherings or large parties with accommodations for up to 150 guests. Private dining menus feature fresh seafood and prime steaks with our signature sides and freshly baked pies. Tuxedo-clad restaurant style service allows guests to select their entree at the time of the event. Our dedicated event planners will ensure your event is both exceptional and effortless. Private dining with versatile table configurations make the space ideal for groups ranging from 30 to 104 guests for a seated dinner or up to 150 for standing receptions. Complete privacy with seating for up to 14 guests, the Boardroom is the perfect room for your next meeting or celebration. Located on the first floor adjacent to the main dining room, Jesse\u2019s Room provides a captivating party space for groups of all sizes. With a maximum capacity of 100 for seated events only, the room captures the look and feel of Joe\u2019s. A lovely, fully-customizable outdoor space providing a view of the Las Vegas Strip within an oasis of trees and topiaries. This unique garden space is perfect for corporate or social receptions of up to 200 guests with a wide variety of set-up options including tenting, staging, and lounge seating (subject to pricing and availability). The larger of our new event spaces, Grace's North is a completely private room accommodating up to 70 for seated events and up to 90 for a reception style event. Full AV, onsite bar and pre-function space.  Grace's South is a completely private space accommodating up to 30 for seated events and up for 40 for a reception style event. It offers multiple table configurations, full AV and pre function space.  Grace's Room accommodates up to 110 for seated functions and 125 for reception style events. Enjoy full AV, multiple flat screen tv's, an on-site bar and pre-function space.  Click on a room to learn more AV Equipment | Flat Screen TV | Laptop Connections | Wireless Microphone  Stella Morales joined the Joe's team in 2022, bringing with her a 17+ year career in the hospitality\u00a0industry.\u00a0Her\u00a0experience ranges from running a day cruise ship, to planning weddings, social and corporate events. With a drive and tenacity to succeed, as well as the desire to exceed the expectations of the clients, Stella says what she enjoys most about her job is painting the picture for the client to help them really understand the possibilities\u00a0for their special event. She excels\u00a0in conducting needs assessments and providing unique solutions to unusual requests and looks forward to helping you plan your next occasion at Joe's.\u00a0 Mike has been a member of the Joe's team since 2016 - originally joining as a server in the main dining room before transitioning to the private events team where he most recently worked as a banquet captain.  His broad experience through multiple roles in the restaurant has given him invaluable insight and knowledge into what it takes to make an event special. From corporate functions to weddings, Mike takes pride in every event he puts together and always looks forward to hearing feedback from his guests. A native of Chicago, Mike has called Las Vegas home for the last nine years. When not at work, you can find him on the golf course, traveling and enjoying the many wonderful restaurants that Las Vegas has to offer.   \r\n Valet Parking Available or  Book with Spothero Sunday - Thursday 11:30am - 9:00pm Friday - Saturday 11:30am - 10:00pm We use cookies to provide the best experience on our website. By continuing to use our site you agree to  our updated privacy policy . for every $100 in gift cards you buy No holiday meal\u00a0is complete without a delicious pie from Joe's. Orders must be placed by Saturday, November 18 for pickup on Tuesday, November 21 or Wednesday, November 22.", "size": 47243, "depth": 2, "download_timeout": 180.0, "download_slot": "www.joes.net", "download_latency": 0.8312709331512451, "status": 200, "links_url": "https://www.joes.net/las-vegas/private-parties/#main@@https://www.joes.net/chicago/@@https://www.joes.net/las-vegas/@@https://www.joes.net/dc/@@https://www.joes.net@@https://www.joes.net/las-vegas@@https://www.joes.net/las-vegas/reservations/@@https://www.joes.net/las-vegas/menu/@@https://www.joes.net/las-vegas/private-parties/@@https://www.joes.net/las-vegas/carry-out/@@https://www.joes.net/las-vegas/whats-crackin/@@https://joes.cashstar.com/@@https://www.joes.net/las-vegas/menu/private-dining/@@https://www.tripleseat.com@@https://goo.gl/maps/DyA1ncbZj5m@@https://spothero.app.link/ts1p2NqSe1?kind=destination&id=84051&$3p=a_hasoffers&$affiliate_json=http%3A%2F%2Ftracking.spothero.com%2Faff_c%3Foffer_id%3D1%26aff_id%3D1568%26source%3Djoesseafoodlasvegas%26format%3Djson@@https://goo.gl/maps/DyA1ncbZj5m@@https://www.joes.net/las-vegas/newsletter-mobile-club@@https://www.joes.net/las-vegas/contact@@https://www.facebook.com/joesvegas/@@https://twitter.com/joesvegas@@https://www.instagram.com/joesseafood/@@