e flavors of Burgundy wines are best enjoyed in their own signature Burgundy wine glass. With a medium-wide bowl and a tapered lip, these glasses allow for optimal aeration and enjoyment. To make a reservation, use the widget below or call  Joe's Las Vegas at  (702) 792-9222 .\n\t\t\t Valet Parking Available or  Book with Spothero Sunday - Thursday 11:30am - 9:00pm Friday - Saturday 11:30am - 10:00pm We use cookies to provide the best experience on our website. By continuing to use our site you agree to  our updated privacy policy . for every $100 in gift cards you buy No holiday meal\u00a0is complete without a delicious pie from Joe's. Orders must be placed by Saturday, November 18 for pickup on Tuesday, November 21 or Wednesday, November 22.", "size": 42131, "depth": 3, "download_timeout": 180.0, "download_slot": "www.joes.net", "download_latency": 0.695462703704834, "status": 200, "links_url": "https://www.joes.net/whats-crackin/sips-tips-olivier-leflaive-3/#main@@https://www.joes.net/chicago/@@https://www.joes.net/las-vegas/@@https://www.joes.net/dc/@@https://www.joes.net@@https://www.joes.net/las-vegas@@https://www.joes.net/las-vegas/reservations/@@https://www.joes.net/las-vegas/menu/@@https://www.joes.net/las-vegas/private-parties/@@https://www.joes.net/las-vegas/carry-out/@@https://www.joes.net/las-vegas/whats-crackin/@@https://joes.cashstar.com/@@https://goo.gl/maps/DyA1ncbZj5m@@https://spothero.app.link/ts1p2NqSe1?kind=destination&id=84051&$3p=a_hasoffers&$affiliate_json=http%3A%2F%2Ftracking.spothero.com%2Faff_c%3Foffer_id%3D1%26aff_id%3D1568%26source%3Djoesseafoodlasvegas%26format%3Djson@@https://goo.gl/maps/DyA1ncbZj5m@@https://www.joes.net/las-vegas/newsletter-mobile-club@@https://www.joes.net/las-vegas/contact@@https://www.facebook.com/joesvegas/@@https://twitter.com/joesvegas@@https://www.instagram.com/joesseafood/@@https://www.lettuce.com@@https://joes.cashstar.com@@https://harri.com/LEYE?filters=brands%253D4489669%25252C4489662%25252C4489657@@https: