oom, Jesse\u2019s Room offers semi-private seating for up to 24 guests. Our most intimate dining space for business and social gatherings, Michael\u2019s Room seats up to 16 guests privately or 32 as a semi-private dining room. The room comes equipped with a 48\" monitor and DirectTV.  Complete privacy with seating for up to 24 guests, the Boardroom is the perfect place for your next meeting or celebration. The room is equipped with a 72\" monitor with laptop connectivity, DirectTV and conference telephone. Table linens are available upon request.  Click on a room to learn more AV Equipment | Flat Screen TV | Laptop Connections | High-speed Wireless Internet | Wireless Microphone  Joe's has been Matt's home since the day the restaurant opened in 2000.  Originally a server in the main dining room, he transitioned to private events where he worked as a banquet captain for years.  His many years of experience helping guests with their needs on the night of their special event, has given him invaluable insight into what it takes to plan a special event.  From social gatherings to corporate functions, Matt values every opportunity to show off the skills, execution and passion that Joe's Private Events team brings to the table.\r\n\r\nHaving grown up in Chicago, Matt has spent many summers at the lakefront and many winters exploring the city's exciting culinary landscape. When not at the restaurant, he happily divides his time between his family, his friends, and his loyal dog Gus. James has been a part of the Lettuce Entertain You family since 2007, beginning as a server and banquet captain at Joe\u2019s Seafood, Prime Steak & Stone Crab in Las Vegas. A highlight of his time working in Vegas was helping guests have the meal of a lifetime, and creating unique experience they could look back on for years to come. Growing up in Kentucky, where hospitality and personability are paramount, James found that his attention to detail and close connections with customers helped fuel his love of service.  \r\n\r\nNow, as the Special Events & Private Dining Manager for Joe\u2019s Chicago, James looks forward to enfusing your private party or event with the best of what you\u2019ve come to know and love about Joe\u2019s.  Whether you\u2019re hosting an important client or celebrating a 50th wedding anniversary, James and his seasoned service team are dedicated to crafting a dining experience to meet all of your individual needs and exceed your expectations.  The heart of Joe\u2019s is celebrating a timeless family tradition. James truly looks forward to helping you create a tradition of your own. Valet Parking Available or  Book with Spothero Sunday - Thursday 11:30am - 9:30pm Friday - Saturday 11:30am - 10:00pm We use cookies to provide the best experience on our website. By continuing to use our site you agree to  our updated privacy policy . for every $100 in gift cards you buy Place your order for a la carte carryout and whole pies for pickup November 21 or 22. Pie orders must be placed by 11/17.", "size": 47304, "depth": 2, "download_timeout": 180.0, "download_slot": "www.joes.net", "download_latency": 0.8421659469604492, "status": 200, "links_url": "https://www.joes.net/chicago/private-parties/#main@@https://www.joes.net/chicago/@@https://www.joes.net/las-vegas/@@https://www.joes.net/dc/@@https://www.joes.net@@https://www.joes.net/chicago@@https://www.joes.net/chicago/reservations/@@https://www.joes.net/chicago/menu/@@https://www.joes.net/chicago/private-parties/@@https://www.joes.net/chicago/carry-out-delivery/@@https://www.joes.net/chicago/whats-crackin/@@https://joes.cashstar.com/@@https://www.joes.net/chicago/menu/private-dining/@@https://www.tripleseat.com@@https://goo.gl/maps/krZMxiApUk52@@https://spothero.app.link/ts1p2NqSe1?kind=destination&id=27908&$3p=a_hasoffers&$affiliate_json=http%3A%2F%2Ftracking.spothero.com%2Faff_c%3Foffer_id%3D1%26aff_id%3D1568%26source%3Djoesseafoodchicago%26format%3Djson@@https://goo.gl/maps/krZMxiApUk5